text: Byggnadsarbetaren is the official magazine of the builders union. The magazine was established in 1949. It is published eight times a year. It is based in Stockholm, Sweden. Kenneth Pettersson is the editor-in-chief of the magazine. In 2012 the circulation of Byggnadsarbetaren was 108,300 copies. ==References== ==External links== * Official website Category:1949 establishments in Sweden Category:Magazines established in 1949 Category:Magazines published in Stockholm Category:Magazines published in Sweden Category:Swedish-language magazines Category:Professional and trade magazines Category:Eight times annually magazines
